trans-unit.source: Passed to custom WSDL exporters and importers to enable customization of the metadata export and import processes for a contract.
trans-unit.target: Passado para exportadores e importadores WSDL personalizados para habilitar a personalização dos processos de importação e exportação de metadados para um contrato.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext> object to examine and modify items that are to be converted to or from WSDL.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext> objeto para examinar e modificar os itens que devem ser convertidos para ou de WSDL.

trans-unit.source: When exporting metadata a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext> object is passed to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Ao exportar metadados de um <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext> objeto é passado para o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A> e <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A> métodos.

trans-unit.source: Use the various methods and properties to obtain metadata objects that you can use to examine and modify to alter the published WSDL.
trans-unit.target: Use os vários métodos e propriedades para obter objetos de metadados que você pode usar para examinar e modificar para alterar o WSDL publicado.

trans-unit.source: When importing metadata a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext> object is passed to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Ao importar metadados de um <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext> objeto é passado para o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A> e <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A> métodos.

trans-unit.source: Use the various methods and properties to obtain metadata objects that you can use to examine and modify the imported metadata.
trans-unit.target: Use os vários métodos e propriedades para obter objetos de metadados que você pode usar para examinar e modificar os metadados importados.
